<br />
<br />I haven't worked on it in several weeks [not sure where my energy/motivation/time is going these days--probably the lack of sleep and family demands] but the last thing I was working on was making my emulation match traces from Visual2A03.  I posted several threads about things that Visual2A03 reveals that I thought were assumed/unknown.  Alas most of that is too esoteric to be widely interesting, so I retreated to my git repository to enhance my emulator in hopes of putting out a new release.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
